 Mark two objects on each frame; click once on the projectile cart and once
 on the target cart.
 The data table should contain five columns with the values of time, x and
 y positions of the projectile cart, and x and y positions of the target
 cart.
 Note: Since this is a horizontal 1D collision the y-coordinates are of
 no interest.
 They should be constant for each frame.
 If they are not, consult your instructor.
\layout Standard

